data.description: PRICE REDUCED!! Honey Stop The Car! This Pristine Villa is special  with great Features.This 3 Bedroom 2 bath has a Den/office/ as the third bedroom. With the open floor plan and volume ceilings and inviting private lanai view, this home feels larger than the square footage shows. Ample 2 car garage. NO CDD or BOND! List price reduced to $295,000 a value not to be beat! HOA over 55. Association approval of buyer IS MANDATORY  Maintenance free exterior. Extra 2 space parking.  Lakeside Landings has a relaxed Lifestyle avoiding the high traffic that the Villages has, yet is close to Brownwood,and Lake Sumter Landings. Our community boasts of a 13,000 sq. ft Clubhouse with private fitness center, billiard room, card room, banquet Hall with dance floor, stage and catering kitchen. Our resort style swimming pool with water falls and fountain is the focal point of our spa ,and inviting cabana. Also on grounds is a putting green, Pickle ball and tennis courts, playground,dog park with a second smaller pool and hot tub. Imagine safe quiet stroll throughout without noisy traffic. Lots of leisure activity without the congestion. To visit this beautiful home  hit call button for visitor gate entrance. Once through the gate go straight on Regatta. 10050 Regatta home is on right.  There is just a $124 fire bill and no property tax showing due to veteran ,disability and homestead.
